{"tid":2215390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鬼祟改警例 「不影響行動」才配合採訪","createTime":"2020-09-24T03:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:33:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b36bb5a2820221bcd4a2e37001b302d2226d0692","tid":2215390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/FY2SBIG7RJDKHKXNSMU6RG5CQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FFY2SBIG7RJDKHKXNSMU6RG5CQQ%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=fdeceeaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FFY2SBIG7RJDKHKXNSMU6RG5CQQ%2F&h=f531aa14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/FY2SBIG7RJDKHKXNSMU6RG5CQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鬼祟改警例<br />\n「不影響行動」才配合採訪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5Th-2M70S9M0drZeTmYNcK_oOPQ=/5318x4202/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D2UODHCW6RA7VMSXVQI5CXOVQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5Th-2M70S9M0drZeTmYNcK_oOPQ%3D%2F5318x4202%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD2UODHCW6RA7VMSXVQI5CXOVQM.jpg&h=a06b3eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■楊健興斥警方聲稱尊重新聞自由的說法頓成空話。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方日前去信四個新聞業界團體稱會修改《警察通例》中「傳媒代表」定義外，原來更在未有知會傳媒下，同時鬼祟修改《警察通例》中有關警員配合傳媒工作的要求，由過去在場警員「須」以互讓互諒的態度，盡量配合傳媒工作，以及不應妨礙傳媒的攝錄工作，改為「在不影響行動效率的情況下」才盡量配合傳媒工作。記協斥警自我加大權力，「以後可以想點就點！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：郭嘉銓稱方便工作 楊健興：唔阻攝錄當幫忙  警篩選傳媒 記協擬覆核<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊健興斥警可為所欲為<br />\n<br />\n根據警方公開的《警察通例》，有關警方如何配合傳媒工作章節的原先寫明：「在事發現場的人員，。。。。。。。。。，有關修訂已在昨天在未諮詢傳媒意見情況下，由警方單方面宣告生效。<br />\n<br />\n記協主席楊健興認為，警方上述改動，等於為警方日後如何配合傳媒工作訂立「前設條件」，。。。。。。。。。。。，更有效及快捷地辨識傳媒身份，聲言會繼續積極與新聞界溝通。"},{"pid":"a110db4433e17f3bf34bd9366f8c30d56a5a8df1","tid":2215390,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973182cc98294711f9fa4edd1e7ee1efe559821b","tid":2215390,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"不影響出糧&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db53965f297b734dd278bc504a2b665cf9dbb34","tid":2215390,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"其實記者點樣影響到你地做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc9204b2ca18a591f6074c3e68f8dd4bf7d7e1a","tid":2215390,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db53965f297b734dd278bc504a2b665cf9dbb34","tid":2215390,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"其實記者點樣影響到你地做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"有機會影到罪證就叫影響啦"},{"pid":"ab574df8f38d4459526cf61ac00e7be32be8e205","tid":2215390,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"而家砌唔到生豬肉<br />\n應該係多主流同獨立/學生記者影到好多片<br />\n證明事主真係無辜<br />\n又入唔到罪<br />\n緊係唔中意你地咁多傳媒影哂真相出黎啦"},{"pid":"580d693a2c7b263df9891997b863fc38c14a074d","tid":2215390,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d86b444416719f3781bee2da1966754f6b04be2b","tid":2215390,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc9204b2ca18a591f6074c3e68f8dd4bf7d7e1a","tid":2215390,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db53965f297b734dd278bc504a2b665cf9dbb34","tid":2215390,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"